3
00:01:33,229 --> 00:01:34,030
We succeeded?

4
00:01:34,430 --> 00:01:35,280
Fourth Master,

5
00:01:35,280 --> 00:01:36,710
we did succeed.

6
00:01:37,590 --> 00:01:38,310
Great!

7
00:01:41,479 --> 00:01:42,509
Great!

8
00:01:43,310 --> 00:01:44,840
Do you know what this is called?

9
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:46,680
It's called karma.

10
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:50,300
My good third brother...

11
00:01:51,229 --> 00:01:52,200
He was cruel enough to ruin

12
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:54,070
his own brother's future,

13
00:01:54,759 --> 00:01:55,789
so don't blame me

14
00:01:55,789 --> 00:01:58,039
for making him taste the agony

15
00:01:58,350 --> 00:02:00,070
of losing his true love.

16
00:02:01,180 --> 00:02:02,300
But Fourth Master,

17
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:03,790
that Xie said

18
00:02:04,350 --> 00:02:05,680
they couldn't get out of the city.

19
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:06,640
With no other choice,

20
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:08,560
they can only hide in the capital for now.

21
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:09,150
What?

22
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:10,430
This...

23
00:02:12,030 --> 00:02:13,830
Wh-What else did he say?

24
00:02:14,430 --> 00:02:15,430
He just said...

25
00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:18,000
"Making him taste the agony

26
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:19,400
of losing his true love"?

27
00:02:21,730 --> 00:02:23,200
Third Uncle's true love?

28
00:02:25,030 --> 00:02:28,290
Everyone who is supposed
to be in the mansion is still here.

29
00:02:29,060 --> 00:02:30,380
Could it be Gu Jinzhao?

30
00:02:31,870 --> 00:02:33,070
For the next two days,

31
00:02:33,150 --> 00:02:34,470
put everything else aside

32
00:02:34,470 --> 00:02:36,470
and keep a close eye on Fourth Uncle.

33
00:02:37,150 --> 00:02:37,680
No.

34
00:02:39,810 --> 00:02:41,230
He won't show up himself.

35
00:02:44,190 --> 00:02:45,540
Just keep an eye on Chen Zhong

36
00:02:45,540 --> 00:02:47,140
and see what his next move is.

37
00:02:52,030 --> 00:02:52,590
Hya!

38
00:02:53,310 --> 00:02:54,760
Mr. Jiang has sent a message.

39
00:02:54,760 --> 00:02:56,430
We've found traces of the criminals.

40
00:02:56,430 --> 00:02:58,690
It seems they headed toward the capital.

41
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:27,310
You just

42
00:03:27,310 --> 00:03:28,520
locked her inside like this?

43
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:29,560
With people coming and going,

44
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:31,020
what if someone finds out?

45
00:03:31,430 --> 00:03:32,930
You don't understand.

46
00:03:33,079 --> 00:03:34,750
It's darkest under the lamp.

47
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:36,050
Don't worry.

48
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:37,310
Tomorrow morning,

49
00:03:37,310 --> 00:03:39,360
a human trafficker is coming to see her.

50
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,820
Once she's in their hands,

51
00:03:41,150 --> 00:03:42,480
they have plenty of ways

52
00:03:42,750 --> 00:03:44,150
to erase her traces.

53
00:03:50,190 --> 00:03:50,800
Chen Yi!

54
00:03:51,030 --> 00:03:52,140
Take my calling card

55
00:03:52,140 --> 00:03:53,000
to the Five Wards Military Command

56
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:54,240
and tell them I will arrive shortly.

57
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:54,710
Also,

58
00:03:54,870 --> 00:03:55,590
return to the mansion to fetch my seal.

59
00:03:55,590 --> 00:03:56,030
Hurry!

60
00:03:56,030 --> 00:03:56,520
Yes!

61
00:03:57,710 --> 00:03:58,510
Third Master,

62
00:03:58,910 --> 00:03:59,630
are you going to...

63
00:03:59,630 --> 00:04:00,630
Lock down the city!

64
00:04:00,630 --> 00:04:02,080
Since they are in the city,

65
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:04,010
lock down the capital completely!

66
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:06,090
Close the gates and search!

67
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:12,080
I'll take both.

68
00:04:12,910 --> 00:04:14,170
Forty taels of silver.

69
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:15,500
Not a single coin more.

70
00:04:46,510 --> 00:04:47,240
Follow them.

71
00:04:53,430 --> 00:04:54,390
What are you doing?

72
00:04:54,390 --> 00:04:55,190
Let us go!

73
00:05:01,070 --> 00:05:01,800
Sir,

74
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:03,560
give me some water.

75
00:05:03,880 --> 00:05:05,150
You talk too much.

76
00:05:26,390 --> 00:05:27,240
Don't eat it then.

77
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:28,070
Sir, sir!

78
00:05:29,260 --> 00:05:31,120
This is really terrible.

79
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:32,250
I can't eat it.

80
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:35,580
How about this?

81
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:36,630
Take this thing

82
00:05:36,630 --> 00:05:37,630
on my wrist.

83
00:05:48,159 --> 00:05:49,720
If you take this to a pawnshop,

84
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:51,920
it's worth at least 100 taels of silver.

85
00:05:58,360 --> 00:06:00,830
Look. What's this?

86
00:06:08,300 --> 00:06:09,510
You're really impressive now!

87
00:06:09,510 --> 00:06:10,310
Of course I am.

88
00:06:11,850 --> 00:06:14,050
[Ji's Pawnshop]

89
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:18,750
Hold on.

90
00:06:19,390 --> 00:06:20,230
Seize

91
00:06:20,270 --> 00:06:21,110
this woman!

92
00:06:21,260 --> 00:06:21,890
You...

93
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:23,390
You...

94
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,870
What are you doing?

95
00:06:26,410 --> 00:06:27,750
This pink pearl

96
00:06:27,830 --> 00:06:29,250
is from the West Sea.

97
00:06:29,590 --> 00:06:31,790
It's the only one in the entire capital.

98
00:06:31,950 --> 00:06:32,920
It's a dowry gift

99
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:33,560
from our Old Madam

100
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:34,720
to our Eldest Miss.

101
00:06:34,870 --> 00:06:35,510
Tell me!

102
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:37,500
Why is it in your hands?

103
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:38,240
I...

104
00:06:39,750 --> 00:06:42,070
I don't know!

105
00:06:44,830 --> 00:06:45,360
Madam,

106
00:06:45,720 --> 00:06:47,120
this is the Young Master.

107
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:48,040
You may leave.

108
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:55,050
I heard you want someone

109
00:06:55,310 --> 00:06:57,120
with good looks,

110
00:06:58,120 --> 00:06:59,950
who is literate,

111
00:07:00,310 --> 00:07:03,070
and comes from a good family.

112
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:05,310
This kind of girl,

113
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:06,720
I do have one.

114
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:08,720
However,

115
00:07:09,310 --> 00:07:10,600
she's not cheap.

116
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:12,050
Name your price.

117
00:07:15,390 --> 00:07:16,720
Two hundred taels it is.

118
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:20,630
[50 taels]

119
00:07:20,650 --> 00:07:23,160
[Great Yan Bank
General Circulation Banknotes]

120
00:07:25,200 --> 00:07:26,700
Why is this only 150 taels?

121
00:07:31,270 --> 00:07:32,670
This jade pendant of mine

122
00:07:32,680 --> 00:07:34,630
is worth at least 50 taels.

123
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:37,380
However...

124
00:07:38,900 --> 00:07:40,560
you have to let me see her first

125
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:42,180
before I give it to you.

126
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:44,530
You want to inspect the goods, huh?

127
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:45,270
Alright.

128
00:07:45,870 --> 00:07:47,270
Then come with me.

129
00:07:56,310 --> 00:07:58,159
She is right inside.

130
00:08:01,520 --> 00:08:02,330
Let's go.

131
00:08:16,270 --> 00:08:17,160
Right now...

132
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:19,290
they've already been drugged.

133
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:21,120
It'll be easier for you

134
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:23,360
to take them away later.

135
00:08:24,430 --> 00:08:26,000
The drug won't hurt.

136
00:08:57,630 --> 00:08:58,270
Move!

137
00:08:59,390 --> 00:09:00,660
Third Uncle's voice?

138
00:09:09,910 --> 00:09:10,630
Don't run!

139
00:09:34,150 --> 00:09:34,810
Don't move!

140
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:18,840
It's alright now.

141
00:10:19,630 --> 00:10:21,490
-Third Master...
-It's alright.

142
00:10:22,550 --> 00:10:23,960
I was so scared!

143
00:10:24,720 --> 00:10:25,720
It's alright now.

144
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:27,600
It's alright. It's alright.

145
00:10:34,630 --> 00:10:35,490
How do you feel?

146
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:38,270
Third Master...

147
00:10:42,870 --> 00:10:44,720
Jinzhao? Jinzhao!

148
00:11:00,150 --> 00:11:00,870
Stop!

149
00:11:01,870 --> 00:11:02,670
Stop!

150
00:11:06,790 --> 00:11:07,760
Don't pull me!

151
00:11:11,510 --> 00:11:12,610
Get away!

152
00:11:12,640 --> 00:11:14,010
Go to hell!

153
00:11:14,630 --> 00:11:15,740
Go to hell!

154
00:11:37,910 --> 00:11:38,840
Young Master...

155
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:42,770
She saw our faces.

156
00:11:44,260 --> 00:11:45,110
I know.

157
00:12:00,120 --> 00:12:00,940
Young Master,

158
00:12:01,270 --> 00:12:02,200
don't be afraid.

159
00:12:04,870 --> 00:12:06,200
I killed her.

160
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:09,050
Don't be afraid.

161
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:11,730
Don't be afraid, Young Master.

162
00:12:24,490 --> 00:12:26,380
Gu Jinzhao was taken away?

163
00:12:26,510 --> 00:12:27,220
Yes.

164
00:12:27,350 --> 00:12:28,750
In a moment of desperation, Lord Chen

165
00:12:28,750 --> 00:12:30,080
contacted the Five Wards Military Command

166
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:31,720
and locked all the city gates.

167
00:12:31,720 --> 00:12:33,600
They claimed to be catching bandits

168
00:12:33,600 --> 00:12:34,940
and searched from house to house.

169
00:12:34,940 --> 00:12:36,690
In the end, they found them in a courtyard

170
00:12:36,690 --> 00:12:38,490
in the southern part of the city.

171
00:12:51,790 --> 00:12:53,960
Gu Jinzhao, is this the man you chose?

172
00:12:59,130 --> 00:12:59,700
You,

173
00:13:00,290 --> 00:13:01,310
take a few men

174
00:13:02,670 --> 00:13:03,960
and my warrant

175
00:13:04,790 --> 00:13:06,600
to the Five Wards Military Command

176
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:07,910
and bring the villains
who kidnapped Gu Jinzhao

177
00:13:07,910 --> 00:13:09,000
to me.

178
00:13:10,120 --> 00:13:11,180
Tell them this case

179
00:13:11,510 --> 00:13:13,310
will be tried by Xuanfeng Guard.

180
00:13:13,830 --> 00:13:14,310
Yes.

181
00:13:17,750 --> 00:13:19,000
Bring out the prisoners

182
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:19,870
caught yesterday.

183
00:13:19,870 --> 00:13:20,390
Yes.

184
00:13:23,750 --> 00:13:24,360
My Lord.

185
00:13:24,690 --> 00:13:25,820
No need to follow me.

186
00:13:30,850 --> 00:13:34,610
[Ancestral Virtues, Our Guiding Light]

187
00:13:32,510 --> 00:13:34,720
Why aren't they back yet?

188
00:13:35,600 --> 00:13:36,150
Hupo.

189
00:13:36,670 --> 00:13:37,870
Go and check the door.

190
00:13:37,910 --> 00:13:38,440
Yes.

191
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:40,600
Mother,

192
00:13:41,200 --> 00:13:41,960
why don't we go back

193
00:13:41,960 --> 00:13:43,440
inside and sit down to wait?

194
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:44,200
Seriously,

195
00:13:44,960 --> 00:13:47,630
Yanyun's wife is too headstrong.

196
00:13:48,320 --> 00:13:49,550
When a newly married woman

197
00:13:49,550 --> 00:13:51,200
visits her natal family, she usually goes
to her father's side—

198
00:13:51,200 --> 00:13:52,150
yet she

199
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:54,660
went to her mother's family instead.

200
00:13:54,840 --> 00:13:55,670
See?

201
00:13:56,150 --> 00:13:57,390
Now something has happened.

202
00:13:57,390 --> 00:13:59,360
Mother, please calm down.

203
00:13:59,960 --> 00:14:01,000
Yanyun's wife

204
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:02,510
is indeed a bit willful.

205
00:14:03,150 --> 00:14:03,790
But

206
00:14:04,000 --> 00:14:04,750
she couldn't have known

207
00:14:04,750 --> 00:14:06,080
she would be kidnapped.

208
00:14:06,600 --> 00:14:08,480
Fortunately, she was rescued,

209
00:14:08,510 --> 00:14:09,240
right?

210
00:14:10,030 --> 00:14:11,030
It's just that...

211
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:13,620
she was missing for a whole day and night.

212
00:14:13,670 --> 00:14:15,240
Who knows what happened?

213
00:14:17,200 --> 00:14:19,510
She is the wife
of a Grand Secretary, after all.

214
00:14:19,510 --> 00:14:20,440
In the future,

215
00:14:20,750 --> 00:14:23,110
there will definitely be plenty of gossip.

216
00:14:23,110 --> 00:14:25,600
That's exactly what I'm afraid of.

217
00:14:25,790 --> 00:14:27,320
If people gossip about her,

218
00:14:28,750 --> 00:14:30,750
it will also drag our Yanyun down.

219
00:14:31,480 --> 00:14:32,440
Seriously!

220
00:14:42,750 --> 00:14:43,240
Master.

221
00:14:43,510 --> 00:14:44,430
How was it?

222
00:14:44,790 --> 00:14:45,990
They were all caught.

223
00:14:46,360 --> 00:14:47,150
I took a shortcut

224
00:14:47,150 --> 00:14:48,790
to come back and bring you the news.

225
00:14:48,790 --> 00:14:49,440
Master,

226
00:14:49,670 --> 00:14:51,240
before Third Master traces it back to us,

227
00:14:51,240 --> 00:14:52,340
let's run.

228
00:14:52,840 --> 00:14:53,900
If we don't run now,

229
00:14:54,550 --> 00:14:55,510
it'll be too late.

230
00:14:55,510 --> 00:14:56,150
It's over.

231
00:14:57,440 --> 00:14:58,700
We are totally doomed.

232
00:14:59,440 --> 00:15:00,240
They're here!

233
00:15:00,390 --> 00:15:01,360
They're here!

234
00:15:04,440 --> 00:15:05,000
Master.

235
00:15:06,240 --> 00:15:07,080
Jinzhao is back.

236
00:15:07,080 --> 00:15:08,140
Let's go there too.

237
00:15:09,870 --> 00:15:10,720
You go.

238
00:15:11,080 --> 00:15:11,630
I...

239
00:15:12,360 --> 00:15:13,690
I need to go out.

240
00:15:13,870 --> 00:15:15,120
Go out? To where?

241
00:15:15,750 --> 00:15:17,150
Chen Zhong just sent word

242
00:15:17,240 --> 00:15:18,030
that the
Southern Metropolitan Administration

243
00:15:18,030 --> 00:15:20,200
will issue 2 million
extra salt certificates next month.

244
00:15:20,200 --> 00:15:21,800
I must go there immediately.

245
00:15:21,840 --> 00:15:23,750
Chen Zhong, get the carriage ready.

246
00:15:23,750 --> 00:15:24,880
Yes, Fourth Master.

247
00:15:27,120 --> 00:15:27,630
Wait.

248
00:15:27,750 --> 00:15:28,970
Is it that urgent?

249
00:15:29,080 --> 00:15:31,010
Can't you leave tomorrow morning?

250
00:15:31,080 --> 00:15:32,030
What do you know?

251
00:15:49,510 --> 00:15:50,270
Mother...

252
00:15:50,440 --> 00:15:50,910
Well...

253
00:15:51,270 --> 00:15:51,750
It's...

254
00:15:53,790 --> 00:15:54,960
You'd better put me down.

255
00:15:54,960 --> 00:15:56,090
I'll walk by myself.

256
00:15:57,000 --> 00:15:57,670
Mother,

257
00:15:58,440 --> 00:15:59,870
Jinzhao just got a fright

258
00:15:59,870 --> 00:16:01,000
and sprained her ankle.

259
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:03,000
I'll take her back to her room first.

260
00:16:04,150 --> 00:16:05,210
Go back to her room.

261
00:16:10,720 --> 00:16:11,390
Yunting.

262
00:16:12,840 --> 00:16:13,640
Young Master,

263
00:16:14,080 --> 00:16:15,240
don't you think

264
00:16:16,840 --> 00:16:18,000
I look like a joke?

265
00:16:26,120 --> 00:16:27,850
How could there be such a thing?

266
00:16:28,320 --> 00:16:29,550
Shameless.

267
00:16:30,150 --> 00:16:30,870
Mother,

268
00:16:31,510 --> 00:16:32,440
Yanyun

269
00:16:32,960 --> 00:16:34,630
is obviously doing this on purpose.

270
00:16:34,630 --> 00:16:35,670
On purpose?

271
00:16:36,600 --> 00:16:38,080
This is our home.

272
00:16:38,310 --> 00:16:40,370
Is there a need to play so many tricks?

273
00:16:40,390 --> 00:16:41,320
Seriously.

274
00:16:42,400 --> 00:16:44,450
A good man has been led astray.

275
00:16:48,150 --> 00:16:49,680
As for what happened today,

276
00:16:49,910 --> 00:16:52,670
no one is allowed to mention it
in the future.

277
00:16:53,120 --> 00:16:53,840
Yes.

278
00:16:55,600 --> 00:16:56,840
If anyone

279
00:16:57,240 --> 00:16:58,720
dares to gossip

280
00:16:59,600 --> 00:17:00,800
and I hear about it,

281
00:17:01,550 --> 00:17:02,810
there will be no trial—

282
00:17:02,910 --> 00:17:05,109
they will be beaten to death on the spot.

283
00:17:05,349 --> 00:17:06,510
-Yes.
-Yes.

284
00:17:06,920 --> 00:17:07,980
It's getting late.

285
00:17:08,480 --> 00:17:09,609
Everyone, dismiss.

286
00:17:21,160 --> 00:17:22,220
Just sit, alright?

287
00:17:24,310 --> 00:17:26,240
Let me help you take off your shoes.

288
00:17:30,110 --> 00:17:30,970
How do you feel?

289
00:17:31,550 --> 00:17:32,720
You suffered a lot.

290
00:17:33,200 --> 00:17:34,920
You were abducted this time,

291
00:17:35,750 --> 00:17:37,790
so it's inevitable
that people will gossip.

292
00:17:37,790 --> 00:17:39,390
By carrying you in like this,

293
00:17:40,310 --> 00:17:42,240
if there are still any blind fools,

294
00:17:42,550 --> 00:17:43,350
then don't blame me

295
00:17:43,350 --> 00:17:44,680
for not warning them.

296
00:17:44,750 --> 00:17:45,550
Third Master.

297
00:17:52,070 --> 00:17:53,200
