Third Madam.

586
00:29:28,350 --> 00:29:29,400
Prime Minister Wang's residence

587
00:29:29,400 --> 00:29:30,830
just sent an invitation,

588
00:29:31,400 --> 00:29:32,650
inviting Third Madam

589
00:29:32,830 --> 00:29:35,630
to their residence for tea
the day after tomorrow.

590
00:29:37,750 --> 00:29:38,480
Got it.

591
00:29:48,700 --> 00:29:53,630
[Ancestral Virtues, Our Guiding Light]

592
00:29:54,110 --> 00:29:55,170
How is your injury?

593
00:29:59,070 --> 00:29:59,880
I'm fine now.

594
00:30:00,590 --> 00:30:01,750
Have they caught the mastermind

595
00:30:01,750 --> 00:30:02,810
who kidnapped you?

596
00:30:04,110 --> 00:30:05,270
Third Master is still investigating.

597
00:30:05,270 --> 00:30:06,730
I didn't ask much about it.

598
00:30:08,590 --> 00:30:10,200
It was really a stroke of luck this time.

599
00:30:10,200 --> 00:30:12,060
If Third Uncle had been any later,

600
00:30:13,200 --> 00:30:14,000
you might have

601
00:30:14,480 --> 00:30:15,510
been killed.

602
00:30:18,410 --> 00:30:19,670
I really didn't expect

603
00:30:19,930 --> 00:30:22,390
that you would choose
to marry him in the end.

604
00:30:23,200 --> 00:30:25,660
Is it because of
his high position and power?

605
00:30:26,550 --> 00:30:27,550
But in my heart,

606
00:30:28,480 --> 00:30:30,400
you shouldn't be that kind of person.

607
00:30:30,400 --> 00:30:32,240
I don't know what you're talking about.

608
00:30:32,240 --> 00:30:33,200
I have something to do,

609
00:30:33,200 --> 00:30:34,330
so I'll leave first.

610
00:30:34,940 --> 00:30:35,750
Are you so unwilling

611
00:30:35,750 --> 00:30:36,480
to talk to me?

612
00:30:40,240 --> 00:30:41,720
What are you talking about?

613
00:30:41,720 --> 00:30:43,250
I'm just in a hurry to go out.

614
00:30:43,790 --> 00:30:44,390
By the way,

615
00:30:45,400 --> 00:30:47,030
since I'm married to Third Master,

616
00:30:47,030 --> 00:30:48,690
you should call me Third Aunt.

617
00:31:00,790 --> 00:31:01,200
You...

618
00:31:04,310 --> 00:31:04,960
Sorry.

619
00:31:06,160 --> 00:31:07,820
I accidentally stepped on it.

620
00:31:09,750 --> 00:31:10,400
Forget it.

621
00:31:10,750 --> 00:31:12,080
I don't want it anymore.

622
00:31:14,530 --> 00:31:19,570
[Ancestral Virtues, Our Guiding Light]

623
00:31:26,200 --> 00:31:27,000
Young Master,

624
00:31:27,240 --> 00:31:28,070
let's go back.

625
00:31:29,510 --> 00:31:30,110
Tomorrow,

626
00:31:30,710 --> 00:31:31,780
take this earring

627
00:31:32,110 --> 00:31:33,040
to a jewelry shop

628
00:31:34,110 --> 00:31:36,170
and ask them to make an identical pair

629
00:31:36,270 --> 00:31:37,400
to give to Gu Jinzhao.

630
00:31:37,400 --> 00:31:38,200
Young Master,

631
00:31:38,270 --> 00:31:39,550
we can't do this.

632
00:31:40,350 --> 00:31:41,300
We can't...

633
00:31:41,790 --> 00:31:43,070
make any more mistakes.

634
00:31:43,070 --> 00:31:44,160
Just go.

635
00:31:45,790 --> 00:31:46,630
For her,

636
00:31:46,920 --> 00:31:47,920
I have already...

637
00:31:56,350 --> 00:31:57,510
Why does she still

638
00:31:57,510 --> 00:31:59,040
act like nothing happened?

639
00:32:01,830 --> 00:32:03,550
So there is such a tea party.

640
00:32:05,550 --> 00:32:06,160
What?

641
00:32:06,440 --> 00:32:07,240
You want to go?

642
00:32:07,920 --> 00:32:09,180
You don't want me to go?

643
00:32:09,310 --> 00:32:10,220
Of course I do.

644
00:32:11,110 --> 00:32:12,570
I'm afraid the Wang family

645
00:32:13,310 --> 00:32:14,710
might play tricks on you.

646
00:32:15,790 --> 00:32:17,720
Does it have to do with the scholars

647
00:32:17,720 --> 00:32:18,680
blocking the road last time?

648
00:32:18,680 --> 00:32:19,240
Yes.

649
00:32:20,610 --> 00:32:21,780
What is wrong

650
00:32:21,920 --> 00:32:22,980
with Wang Xuanfan?

651
00:32:23,160 --> 00:32:24,810
During the relief grain case last time,

652
00:32:24,810 --> 00:32:25,440
he deliberately

653
00:32:25,440 --> 00:32:26,510
framed you

654
00:32:26,750 --> 00:32:28,080
and got you imprisoned.

655
00:32:28,440 --> 00:32:30,400
Why is he doing this again?

656
00:32:31,880 --> 00:32:33,270
After that incident,

657
00:32:33,590 --> 00:32:34,750
I told my mentor

658
00:32:35,000 --> 00:32:37,600
that if we want land reform
across the country,

659
00:32:38,000 --> 00:32:39,780
we must start with ourselves.

660
00:32:40,030 --> 00:32:41,090
Grand Secretaries

661
00:32:41,310 --> 00:32:43,200
must take the initiative
to audit their own families

662
00:32:43,200 --> 00:32:44,640
and clear their own taxes,

663
00:32:44,640 --> 00:32:45,270
so they have the justification

664
00:32:45,270 --> 00:32:46,750
to audit lower-ranking officials.

665
00:32:46,750 --> 00:32:47,640
And lower-ranking officials

666
00:32:47,640 --> 00:32:49,000
must clear their own taxes

667
00:32:49,000 --> 00:32:51,530
before they can audit
the gentry and the rich.

668
00:32:51,920 --> 00:32:53,050
So my mentor ordered

669
00:32:53,310 --> 00:32:55,000
officials of the third-rank and above

670
00:32:55,000 --> 00:32:57,240
to self-inspect
and proactively return ill-gotten gains.

671
00:32:57,240 --> 00:32:58,680
Wang Xuanfan is a famous landlord

672
00:32:58,680 --> 00:32:59,880
in Daming Prefecture.

673
00:32:59,880 --> 00:33:00,920
He had to cough up

674
00:33:00,920 --> 00:33:03,380
tens of thousands of taels of silver
at once.

675
00:33:06,350 --> 00:33:07,200
No wonder.

676
00:33:07,310 --> 00:33:09,830
Cutting off someone's wealth
is like killing their parents.

677
00:33:09,830 --> 00:33:11,090
No wonder he hates you.

678
00:33:13,510 --> 00:33:14,400
So

679
00:33:15,110 --> 00:33:16,330
he came up with an idea

680
00:33:16,640 --> 00:33:18,510
to incite the scholars
to make trouble for me.

681
00:33:18,510 --> 00:33:20,040
Regardless of the outcome,

682
00:33:20,310 --> 00:33:21,640
he wanted to pin the blame

683
00:33:21,640 --> 00:33:22,840
of unfair land reform

684
00:33:23,270 --> 00:33:24,400
on me.

685
00:33:25,590 --> 00:33:28,160
A blemish
is what a Grand Secretary fears most.

686
00:33:28,160 --> 00:33:29,560
With a blemish like this,

687
00:33:29,790 --> 00:33:31,410
if someone holds on to it,

688
00:33:31,550 --> 00:33:32,550
it's very likely

689
00:33:33,310 --> 00:33:35,110
I'll be discharged in disgrace.

690
00:33:38,510 --> 00:33:39,640
I see.

691
00:33:50,680 --> 00:33:52,480
The invitation
has been sent to the Chen Mansion.

692
00:33:52,480 --> 00:33:53,330
Madam Chen said

693
00:33:53,330 --> 00:33:54,790
she will definitely come.

694
00:33:55,720 --> 00:33:56,850
Which Chen Mansion?

695
00:33:57,680 --> 00:33:58,680
Third Mr. Chen's?

696
00:34:01,440 --> 00:34:03,400
The day after tomorrow is the tea party.

697
00:34:03,400 --> 00:34:04,600
I invited Gu Jinzhao.

698
00:34:04,680 --> 00:34:06,030
Why did you invite her?

699
00:34:06,110 --> 00:34:07,910
Do you have nothing better to do?

700
00:34:08,360 --> 00:34:10,320
She is also the wife of a Grand Secretary.

701
00:34:10,320 --> 00:34:12,780
Isn't it right
to invite her to the tea party?

702
00:34:13,000 --> 00:34:13,550
Did something

703
00:34:13,550 --> 00:34:14,630
upset you,

704
00:34:14,960 --> 00:34:16,800
and you came here to take it out on me?

705
00:34:16,800 --> 00:34:18,960
What else could upset me?

706
00:34:19,630 --> 00:34:20,550
Isn't this all because of

707
00:34:20,550 --> 00:34:21,880
your terrible idea?

708
00:34:25,000 --> 00:34:26,070
Alright. All...

709
00:34:26,070 --> 00:34:27,070
All of you, leave.

710
00:34:37,510 --> 00:34:38,960
You told me to incite those scholars

711
00:34:38,960 --> 00:34:40,440
to stop Third Mr. Chen's carriage

712
00:34:40,440 --> 00:34:41,920
and protest the unfair land reform.

713
00:34:41,920 --> 00:34:42,630
And what happened?

714
00:34:42,630 --> 00:34:43,440
Now I've gotten myself

715
00:34:43,440 --> 00:34:44,320
caught up in it.

716
00:34:45,320 --> 00:34:46,980
Third Mr. Chen knows about it?

717
00:34:47,110 --> 00:34:49,310
There's nothing to fear even if he does.

718
00:34:49,360 --> 00:34:49,960
Those scholars

719
00:34:49,960 --> 00:34:51,620
were right in the first place.

720
00:34:52,070 --> 00:34:54,440
The land reform is indeed unfair.

721
00:34:54,670 --> 00:34:56,630
You know nothing!

722
00:34:56,960 --> 00:34:58,030
Do you know what those scholars

723
00:34:58,030 --> 00:34:59,630
are shouting as slogans now?

724
00:34:59,880 --> 00:35:01,590
"Clear the imperial estates

725
00:35:02,000 --> 00:35:04,190
and inventory
His Majesty's private properties."

726
00:35:04,190 --> 00:35:04,880
I told them

727
00:35:04,880 --> 00:35:06,320
to protest against the unfair land reform.

728
00:35:06,320 --> 00:35:07,000
I didn't tell them

729
00:35:07,000 --> 00:35:08,880
to clear His Majesty's land.

730
00:35:09,670 --> 00:35:11,280
So you got scolded by Fu Hailian.

731
00:35:11,280 --> 00:35:12,480
What else could it be?

732
00:35:13,230 --> 00:35:13,920
In front of Third Mr. Chen,

733
00:35:13,920 --> 00:35:15,380
he scolded me harshly.

734
00:35:15,960 --> 00:35:16,880
And look at you.

735
00:35:17,190 --> 00:35:18,790
You even invited Gu Jinzhao.

736
00:35:19,000 --> 00:35:20,400
Aren't you embarrassed?

737
00:35:21,360 --> 00:35:22,960
Why should I be embarrassed?

738
00:35:23,050 --> 00:35:24,980
You are the embarrassed one, okay?

739
00:35:26,280 --> 00:35:27,370
Since this time

740
00:35:27,510 --> 00:35:29,570
you suffered a loss to Third Mr. Chen,

741
00:35:29,800 --> 00:35:32,270
I have even more reason
to invite Gu Jinzhao.

742
00:35:32,400 --> 00:35:32,880
What?

743
00:35:39,230 --> 00:35:41,620
[Where Spring Caresses Jade]

744
00:35:49,950 --> 00:35:51,880
Do you really want to go that badly?

745
00:35:51,920 --> 00:35:53,400
You noticed it?

746
00:35:58,030 --> 00:36:00,160
I'm afraid they'll play tricks on you.

747
00:36:01,440 --> 00:36:02,890
I'm not easy to bully.

748
00:36:03,400 --> 00:36:04,110
True.

749
00:36:05,590 --> 00:36:06,680
I'm more afraid

750
00:36:07,150 --> 00:36:08,750
that you'll clash with them.

751
00:36:08,920 --> 00:36:09,630
What's wrong?

752
00:36:09,630 --> 00:36:11,630
Are you afraid you can't protect me?

753
00:36:14,350 --> 00:36:15,550
Trying to provoke me?

754
00:36:16,000 --> 00:36:17,800
As a dignified Grand Secretary,

755
00:36:17,800 --> 00:36:19,330
although I lack seniority,

756
00:36:19,630 --> 00:36:21,890
I am more than capable of protecting you.

757
00:36:22,630 --> 00:36:23,890
That's fine then.

758
00:36:25,190 --> 00:36:26,810
I want to attend the tea party

759
00:36:26,920 --> 00:36:28,360
not for my own amusement.

760
00:36:29,000 --> 00:36:29,630
It's because

761
00:36:29,630 --> 00:36:31,840
it's the Grand Secretaries' wives'
tea party.

762
00:36:31,840 --> 00:36:33,150
If I don't go,

763
00:36:33,400 --> 00:36:36,130
wouldn't I be
isolating myself from this circle?

764
00:36:36,360 --> 00:36:38,290
That would also bring shame to you.

765
00:36:39,510 --> 00:36:40,400
I know.

766
00:36:42,230 --> 00:36:43,630
These Grand Secretaries' wives

767
00:36:43,630 --> 00:36:45,160
are all more senior than me.

768
00:36:45,670 --> 00:36:46,860
Even Madam Shen

769
00:36:47,000 --> 00:36:48,760
comes from a prestigious family

770
00:36:48,760 --> 00:36:50,760
with a profound family background.

771
00:36:50,920 --> 00:36:51,760
Don't worry.

772
00:36:51,760 --> 00:36:53,320
I won't offend them.

773
00:36:54,920 --> 00:36:55,590
Alright.

774
00:36:56,630 --> 00:36:58,920
Then I'll ask around for you

775
00:36:59,440 --> 00:37:01,150
about these Grand Secretaries' wives'

776
00:37:01,150 --> 00:37:02,440
personalities

777
00:37:02,840 --> 00:37:04,030
and preferences.

778
00:37:04,920 --> 00:37:06,510
Where are you going to ask?

779
00:37:06,670 --> 00:37:08,930
They are all noble ladies in the capital.

780
00:37:09,110 --> 00:37:10,440
If people find out,

781
00:37:10,800 --> 00:37:12,930
they'll laugh at you behind your back.

782
00:37:13,150 --> 00:37:14,320
I have my own ways.

783
00:38:00,190 --> 00:38:01,840
Madam Chen, this way please.

784
00:38:04,080 --> 00:38:05,710
[Integrity, Prudence, Diligence, Harmony]

785
00:38:11,360 --> 00:38:12,280
Madam Fu.

786
00:38:14,070 --> 00:38:15,070
Madam Wang.

787
00:38:17,800 --> 00:38:18,550
Madam Yao.

788
00:38:19,280 --> 00:38:20,150
Madam He.

789
00:38:21,250 --> 00:38:24,530
[Integrity, Prudence, Diligence, Harmony]

790
00:38:21,510 --> 00:38:22,880
Greetings, Madams.

791
00:38:47,960 --> 00:38:49,300
Greetings, Madam Chen.

792
00:38:49,510 --> 00:38:50,570
Please take a seat.

793
00:38:51,900 --> 00:38:55,760
[Integrity, Prudence, Diligence, Harmony]

794
00:38:52,800 --> 00:38:53,690
Miss Qingpu,

795
00:38:54,260 --> 00:38:56,190
please follow me to rest over here.

796
00:39:09,510 --> 00:39:10,760
Look at the new bride.

797
00:39:11,400 --> 00:39:12,960
She's so plain,

798
00:39:13,070 --> 00:39:14,360
yet very beautiful.

799
00:39:14,840 --> 00:39:16,530
Her skin is so dewy.

800
00:39:16,670 --> 00:39:18,070
It is so good to be young.

801
00:39:18,550 --> 00:39:19,970
You flatter me, Madam He.

802
00:39:20,110 --> 00:39:21,170
I don't deserve it.

803
00:39:21,320 --> 00:39:22,510
In terms of looks,

804
00:39:23,000 --> 00:39:24,150
all of you ladies

805
00:39:24,320 --> 00:39:25,740
are much more magnificent.

806
00:39:25,740 --> 00:39:28,970
[Integrity, Prudence, Diligence, Harmony]

807
00:39:26,230 --> 00:39:27,070
I was just

808
00:39:27,230 --> 00:39:28,800
born a little later.

809
00:39:31,440 --> 00:39:32,070
By the way.

810
00:39:32,670 --> 00:39:33,360
Today

811
00:39:33,510 --> 00:39:35,370
is my first time at this tea party.

812
00:39:35,550 --> 00:39:36,760
I prepared gifts

813
00:39:37,000 --> 00:39:38,060
for all the ladies.

814
00:39:40,150 --> 00:39:41,550
Please, no gifts.

815
00:39:42,110 --> 00:39:43,400
This is a tea party,

816
00:39:43,880 --> 00:39:44,590
not a place outside

817
00:39:44,590 --> 00:39:46,360
to curry favor or do business.

818
00:39:47,360 --> 00:39:49,560
The husbands of those of us sitting here

819
00:39:49,670 --> 00:39:51,190
are either Grand Secretaries

820
00:39:51,190 --> 00:39:53,360
or high officials of the Imperial Court.

821
00:39:53,360 --> 00:39:54,000
We ourselves

822
00:39:54,000 --> 00:39:55,880
also hold imperial titles.

823
00:39:56,150 --> 00:39:57,950
If we give each other gifts

824
00:39:58,000 --> 00:39:59,070
and word gets out,

825
00:39:59,280 --> 00:40:01,400
at best we'll be a laughingstock,

826
00:40:01,760 --> 00:40:04,620
and at worst,
we'll give people an excuse to gossip.

827
00:40:06,070 --> 00:40:07,930
When Madam Fu first set this rule,

828
00:40:08,320 --> 00:40:10,190
I thought she was overthinking it.

829
00:40:10,190 --> 00:40:11,190
I didn't expect

830
00:40:11,400 --> 00:40:13,360
someone to actually bring gifts.

831
00:40:15,400 --> 00:40:16,860
It was presumptuous of me.

832
00:40:17,110 --> 00:40:19,360
This is my first time
attending this tea party.

833
00:40:19,360 --> 00:40:21,400
I thought one couldn't go wrong
with being too polite.

834
00:40:21,400 --> 00:40:22,480
I didn't know the tea party

835
00:40:22,480 --> 00:40:23,570
had such rules.

836
00:40:24,000 --> 00:40:24,930
I'm to blame too.

837
00:40:25,440 --> 00:40:27,190
I started preparing gifts

838
00:40:27,320 --> 00:40:28,920
right after receiving
Madam Wang's invitation.

839
00:40:28,920 --> 00:40:29,580
I should

840
00:40:29,670 --> 00:40:31,530
have consulted Madam Wang first.

841
00:40:34,360 --> 00:40:36,290
Since you sent her the invitation,

842
00:40:37,320 --> 00:40:39,580
you should have given her some pointers.

843
00:40:40,710 --> 00:40:41,360
Yes.

844
00:40:42,030 --> 00:40:43,320
I overlooked it.

845
00:40:45,630 --> 00:40:47,050
Is everyone here?

846
00:40:47,210 --> 00:40:54,940
[Integrity, Prudence, Diligence, Harmony]

847
00:40:47,360 --> 00:40:47,840
Yes.

848
00:40:48,400 --> 00:40:49,840
The garden is ready.

849
00:40:49,960 --> 00:40:51,360
Let's all go together.

850
00:41:01,190 --> 00:41:02,190
It doesn't matter.

851
00:41:02,190 --> 00:41:02,920
Don't worry.

852
00:41:05,310 --> 00:41:09,100
[Integrity, Prudence, Diligence, Harmony]

853
00:41:13,510 --> 00:41:14,510
I heard

854
00:41:14,840 --> 00:41:16,960
the Left Vice Minister
of Rites position is vacant.

855
00:41:16,960 --> 00:41:18,070
There have been 2 rounds of recommendation
in the court,

856
00:41:18,070 --> 00:41:19,400
but no one was selected.

857
00:41:21,190 --> 00:41:22,320
If you ask me,

858
00:41:23,510 --> 00:41:25,880
Lord Zeng Ruoyu

859
00:41:26,110 --> 00:41:27,320
is prudent.

860
00:41:27,760 --> 00:41:29,710
He is also a famous scholar,

861
00:41:30,030 --> 00:41:31,560
perfect for this position.

862
00:41:32,320 --> 00:41:33,360
Madam Yao,

863
00:41:33,800 --> 00:41:34,800
what do you think?

864
00:41:38,360 --> 00:41:39,440
My husband

865
00:41:39,510 --> 00:41:41,570
has praised Lord Zeng several times.

866
00:41:42,400 --> 00:41:43,860
For this recommendation,

867
00:41:44,440 --> 00:41:46,570
he will probably recommend Lord Zeng.

868
00:41:47,630 --> 00:41:48,510
That's good.

869
00:41:51,320 --> 00:41:52,590
My husband said

870
00:41:53,230 --> 00:41:56,510
the Hall of Literary Profundity
is short of several drafters.

871
00:41:56,510 --> 00:41:58,640
I remember you have a nephew who became

872
00:41:58,760 --> 00:42:01,280
a palace graduate
in the 35th year of Jingning.

873
00:42:01,280 --> 00:42:02,810
Why not let him give it a try?

874
00:42:04,630 --> 00:42:06,320
Then on behalf of my nephew,

875
00:42:06,320 --> 00:42:07,150
I thank you.

876
00:42:13,320 --> 00:42:14,190
Madam Shen?

877
00:42:17,150 --> 00:42:17,840
You seem a bit

878
00:42:17,840 --> 00:42:19,320
absent-minded today.

879
00:42:20,960 --> 00:42:21,590
Madam.

880
00:42:25,110 --> 00:42:25,670
You know

881
00:42:25,670 --> 00:42:27,110
my husband's temper.

882
00:42:27,280 --> 00:42:28,740
It comes and goes quickly.

883
00:42:29,280 --> 00:42:30,880
Go back and tell Keqian

884
00:42:31,230 --> 00:42:32,590
not to worry too much.

885
00:42:32,960 --> 00:42:34,610
He only gets angry like this

886
00:42:34,800 --> 00:42:35,960
at people he trusts.

887
00:42:36,510 --> 00:42:37,320
I see.

888
00:42:37,550 --> 00:42:38,550
Thank you, Madam.

889
00:42:44,920 --> 00:42:46,070
-Let go of me!
-Let go of me!

890
00:42:46,070 --> 00:42:47,530
-Let go of me!
-Let go of me!

891
00:42:47,590 --> 00:42:48,980
-I'm an Imperial Court official!
-Let go of me!

892
00:42:48,980 --> 00:42:51,280
-Do you have any respect for the law?
-Let go of me!

893
00:42:51,280 --> 00:42:52,360
Let me go!

894
00:42:53,800 --> 00:42:54,920
Commander,

895
00:42:55,110 --> 00:42:56,710
at the inn in the west of the city,

896
00:42:56,710 --> 00:42:58,370
I captured An Deyu and his wife

897
00:42:58,440 --> 00:42:59,690
and found a seal.

898
00:43:00,630 --> 00:43:01,710
Please take a look.

899
00:43:02,440 --> 00:43:03,500
An arrest warrant?

900
00:43:03,880 --> 00:43:05,480
The Three Judiciary Offices
are still investigating.

901
00:43:05,480 --> 00:43:07,540
How could His Majesty issue an edict?

902
00:43:17,880 --> 00:43:18,670
Ye Xian!

903
00:43:18,960 --> 00:43:21,220
Investigating Censor of the Censorate,

904
00:43:21,590 --> 00:43:22,410
An Deyu,

905
00:43:22,550 --> 00:43:25,150
sold government posts, neglected
his duties, and corrupted the law.

906
00:43:25,150 --> 00:43:26,280
By imperial decree,

907
00:43:26,630 --> 00:43:28,430
take him to the imperial prison.

908
00:43:28,920 --> 00:43:29,800
Nonsense!

909
00:43:30,230 --> 00:43:31,700
You are framing me!

910
00:43:32,510 --> 00:43:33,190
Master!

911
00:43:47,160 --> 00:43:50,970
[A Splendid Match]

